Pre-Game Insights: Logan Webb is the workhorse for the Giants and is having a good season.
Zach Eflin has a 2.22 ERA with the Orioles and has 41 strikeouts to just five walks.
Webb has not been good lately, with a 6.75 ERA in September and opponents hitting.362 off him this month.
Eflin has a 2.63 ERA and 1.07 WHIP at home this season.
The Orioles have a good offense that hits for power and does not strike out much.
